:: code.advanceDay [static-storage] {"position":"1550,4050","size":"100,100"}
<!--Advance 1 day algorithm, called with a (display:) command-->

(set: $time's dayCount to it + 1)
(set: $time's day to it + 1)
(if: $time's day > 7)[(set: $time's day to 1)(set: $time's week to it +1)]
(if: $time's week > 4)[(set: $time's week to 1)(set: $time's month to it +1)]
(if: $time's month > 12)[(set: $time's month to 1)(set: $time's year to it +1)]